doc.content: The scientists Morlak, Zota, and Shinski of the Enclave, along with the mysterious Mr. Smith, were determined to use their unparalleled geniuses to create a savior who would usher in the utopia they had long sought to bring into the world. That savior was to be Adan Warlock.
doc.powers: She has identical abilities of Adam Warlock
significantissues: Dreamed that there were another Warlock, got advice from the real Adam Warlock (Warlock #1-3, 2005)
revealed to be the new Warlock herself (Warlock #4, 2005)
